events.text:
I sent word to Marshal Augustus back in Strahmholde about your doings with Bruiseclaw.
With everything situated here at the time being, our troops can fend off further tasks here.
Augustus is waiting for you.
Have you spoke to Marshal Augustus yet?

Hail, we meet again. The kingdom is at peace thanks to your actions.
In spite of all your rightful doings to help secure this great kingdom, we must expand our borders.
